body:
Features and Enhancements

QA Environment
  • Link to QA
    • Added a link to the QA environment from the gear menu in the upper right corner of page.
    • User must use this link to navigate to QA environment.
Maps
  • Coastline clipping
    • Modified maps to clip geographic boundaries at coastlines.
Rank Networks
  • Link expiration
    • Rank Networks session tokens expire after 30 days of inactivity.
